org.zaproxy.zap.model

Interface ContextDataFactory

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ExtensionAuthentication, ExtensionAuthorization, ExtensionForcedUser, ExtensionReauth, ExtensionSessionManagement, ExtensionUserManagement

    public interface ContextDataFactory
    A Context Data Factory implements the logic for persisting and loading data into Contexts into/from a Session, for external (non-core) components.

    • Method Summary

      Methods

      Loads the Context data from the given session.
      void persistContextData(Session session, Context context)
